  "text": "The occurrence of EPS represents an important issue in the deterioration of artworks because their complete elimination from both surface and deep layers are difficult [CITATION_1] . For example, in stoneworks, biofilms induce modifications of the natural porosity of the material, have heavy biocorrosive activity, and can also function as \"pollutant-absorber\" [22] .",
